# Debug First, Implement Later

## Debug Process
1. Investigate thoroughly
2. Get multiple solutions
3. Choose approach
4. Then implement

## Investigation Steps
- Gather all errors
- Check logs
- Review context
- Document findings

## Solution Planning
- List possible fixes
- Evaluate each option
- Consider side effects
- Choose best approach

## Implementation Guidelines
- Document chosen solution
- Test thoroughly
- Verify fix
- Update docs

## Best Practices
- No blind fixes
- Test all solutions
- Document process
- Learn from bugs
